Sales Manager Dubai MEA
Sales Manager Dubai MEA
Location:  --Dubai
Salary:  GBP0 - GBP1 per annumSales Manager – Industrial Automation (Dubai)
Our Client is the world’s largest provider of switching power supplies and a major source for power management solutions, components, visual displays, industrial automation, networking products and renewable energy solutions. Established in 1971, Our Client has sales offices worldwide and manufacturing plants in Taiwan, Thailand, China, Mexico and Europe. As a global leader in power electronics, Our Client is committed to environment protection and has implemented green, lead-free production and recycling and waste management programs for many years. Our Client’s mission continues to be: “To provide innovative energy-saving products for a better quality of life”. To achieve higher business growth, we are looking for a Sales Manager – Industrial Automation based in Dubai to help grow our Industrial Automation Business in the Middle East Region.
The main responsibilities are:
· Grow the business of Industrial Automation products in Middle East Region
· Expand business with current ditstributor
· Expand distribution channels for new products/solutions
· Expand distribution channels for non-performing products/solutions
· Expand/create direct machine OEM customers, including key accounts
· Reinforce enforce cross selling activities for different Our Client products
· Act as the communication link between customers, Our Client EMEA, headquarter in Taiwan and factories in Asia
· Report to the Business Director and provide data for monthly reviews
· Work out strategies per relevant products and market overviews, including competitor analysis
Qualifications:
· Technical degree with commercial knowledge, preferably in Electrical Engineering and Mechanical Engineering
· Experience in Machine Automation sector
· Min. 4 years of working experience in international companies
· Native Arabic speaker with fluent English
· Good interpersonal and communication skills and intercultural awareness
· Good organization, planning, analytical and presentation skills
· Entrepreneur minded with success in new business development
· Commitment to deliver quality work
· Track record of working independently
· Frequent travelling required
· In possession of driving license
Our offer:
A challenging field of activity in a very motivated team, an international business environment and a customer focuses and modern company are waiting for you with lots of space for new ideas and to discover new paths!
